 who were trying to hunt you just ran away.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/0d31478e858dd1cf9b9ba83b1a5bdc35.poster.avif?t=1774203742\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/0d31478e858dd1cf9b9ba83b1a5bdc35.webm?t=1774203742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/0d31478e858dd1cf9b9ba83b1a5bdc35.mp4?t=1774203742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OLD FRIEND NEW ENEMY</h2>There is no getting bored in this game. The new dynamics and objectives that are unlocked when you are cursed and turned into the creature will offer you new experiences until the end of the match.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/763d9d3aa642bd9d7a0ba6a870488f9d.poster.avif?t=1774203742\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/763d9d3aa642bd9d7a0ba6a870488f9d.webm?t=1774203742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/763d9d3aa642bd9d7a0ba6a870488f9d.mp4?t=1774203742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELL OPTIMIZED NEXT GEN GRAPHICS</h2>The best graphics you've ever seen in a Co-Op Horror game. Developed with Unreal Engine 5. Enhanced by Ray Tracing, DLSS, and FSR. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703680/extras/79657009f6d1057384d6c23909167af6.poster.avif?t=1774203742\" width=600 height=232 >